                <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> Caesar divi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Augustus <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>ex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> XX co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> III <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> XI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Cornelio Dolabella <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinander passende Fragmente erhalten. Abmessungen des linken, größeren Fragements: s. o.; Abmessungen des rechten Fragments: 78 x 60.</p>
